definition: some/a few/a little/(following an adjective) slightly ...er
one/1/single/a (article)/as soon as/entire/whole/all/throughout/"one" radical in Chinese characters (Kangxi radical 1)/also pr. [yao1] for greater clarity when spelling out numbers digit by digit
classifier indicating a small amount or small number greater than 1: some, a few, several

sentences.english: Now, there are some immediate bad explanations for this.
sentences.chinese: 馬上就有人提出一些錯漏百出的解釋。

sentences.english: I have nothing but some personal belongings.
sentences.chinese: 我只帶了一些個人用品。

sentences.english: The nature of the stimulus may predispose some children to attention problems.
sentences.chinese: 刺激本身很可能使一些孩子易產生注意力問題。

sentences.english: She ordered gummi bears and a knife a couple hours ago.
sentences.chinese: 幾小時前預定了一些小熊軟糖和一把刀。

sentences.english: Anna Hu joined in as Group Business Director and other hires.
sentences.chinese: 胡曉雲加入擔任業務羣總監，還有一些新成員加盟。

sentences.english: But first, we need to know some terminology.
sentences.chinese: 不過，我們首先需要了解一些術語。

sentences.english: The crowd was disappointed about the lack of enthusiam from the players.
sentences.chinese: 一些缺乏激情的選手們令觀衆大失所望。

sentences.english: Strawberry, blackcurrant, litchi and mango are some popular flavoured yoghurt.
sentences.chinese: 草莓，黑醋栗，荔枝和芒果是一些受歡迎風味的酸奶。

sentences.english: Some of Pedini collections includes nice re-invent of inline kitchen layouts.
sentences.chinese: 一些佩蒂尼的產品包含了重新發明的內嵌廚具佈局。

sentences.english: Performance of coating plate with the special hydrophobic coating solution was better.
sentences.chinese: 採用雙疏塗層溶液塗覆的多孔板相對好一些。

sentences.english: The sources of Chinese medicine are mainly floras, also includes animals and mineral.
sentences.chinese: 中藥的來源主要是植物，也有一些動物和礦物。

sentences.english: He jazzed up the room with some bright red curtains.
sentences.chinese: 他用一些鮮紅的窗簾將房間裝飾得更具生氣。

sentences.english: They will expect a career growth and a magnificent actualization of a number of projects.
sentences.chinese: 他們會預期到職業的成長，一些項目會漂亮的完成。

sentences.english: Some of your red blood cells are deviating from this pattern.
sentences.chinese: 一些你的紅色血球正在脫離這一個典型。

sentences.english: Also eat some fruits, milk and a small amount of soft drinks containing carbonic acid gas.
sentences.chinese: 還可喫一些水果，牛奶以及少量含碳酸氣的飲料。

sentences.english: If my little bit wrong incoming letter word disease sentence invites help correct that.
sentences.chinese: 如果我的來信有一些錯詞病句請幫忙糾正。
